quran[21{c,v,t}:
100,10,Wa hussila maa fis sudoor
100,11,Inna rabbahum bihim yauma 'izil la khabeer
101,1,Al qaari'ah
101,2,Mal qaariah
101,3,Wa maa adraaka mal qaari'ah
101,4,Yauma ya koonun naasu kal farashil mabthooth
101,5,Wa ta koonul jibali kal 'ihnil manfoosh
101,6,Fa-amma man thaqulat mawa zeenuh
101,7,Fahuwa fee 'ishatir raadiyah
101,8,Wa amma man khaffat mawa zeenuh
101,9,Fa-ummuhu haawiyah
101,10,Wa maa adraaka maa hiyah
101,11,Naarun hamiyah
102,1,Al haaku mut takathur
102,2,Hatta zurtumul-maqaabir
102,3,Kalla sawfa ta'lamoon
102,4,Thumma kalla sawfa ta'lamoon
102,5,Kalla law ta'lamoona 'ilmal yaqeen
102,6,Latara-wun nal jaheem
102,7,Thumma latara wunnaha 'ainal yaqeen
102,8,Thumma latus alunna yauma-izin 'anin na'eem
